**TABLE OF CONTENTS**

**1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY**

YGT Holding operates a vertically integrated tomato export business
spanning greenhouse cultivation, international logistics, multi-firm
export structures, and financial management. Currently, the entire
operation runs on **Excel spreadsheets, phone calls, and WhatsApp
messages**. This document presents a comprehensive plan to digitalize
the complete value chain.

+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+
| **SHIPMENTS     | **INVOICES      | **OUTSTANDING   | **MISSING       |
| ANALYZED**      | ANALYZED**      | DEBT**          | REPORTS**       |
|                 |                 |                 |                 |
| **983**         | **461**         | **\$8.3M**      | **90**          |
+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+-----------------+

