**Key Business Rules**

1\. **Standard truck** = 18,100 kg net / 20,500 kg gross (2,400 kg
packaging)

2\. **Shipment code** = DDMM+seq/YY (e.g. 27FV048/25)

3\. **9 roles** edit ONLY their fields. Role-based field permissions
enforced.

4\. **13:00 deadline** for all export documents. After 13:00 = overdue
alert.

5\. **Multi-firm split** --- 2 firms (common: 35.6%) or 3 firms (rare).
Each firm = separate CMR + invoice.

6\. **Gapy Satys** = domestic sale. Buyer's truck at greenhouse.
Generates 1:10 export quota.

7\. **Quota ratio** --- 1 tonne domestic sale = 10 tonnes export quota
(government regulation).

8\. **Missing reports** blocked --- cannot close shipment without sales
report from Arap/Aganazar.

**Key Screens (14 in Prototype)**

Dashboard (5 stats + 4 alerts) · Shipment List (983 rows, 6 filters, 3
views) · Shipment Detail (4 tabs, 13-step timeline) · New Shipment
(multi-role form + \$10K calc) · Tracking Board (Kanban 4 columns) ·
Customers (111 buyers) · Quota Dashboard (1:10 formula visual) · Weekly
Planning (15×6 grid) · Finance · Contracts · Documents · Reports ·
Settings

