Greenhouse (green)** M8-10

**5.3 Why This Order?**

**P3 Export first** --- (1) Most complete analysis (983 shipments
analyzed); (2) Working prototype with 14 screens; (3) Core data
structure that everything depends on; (4) Replaces the biggest pain
point (main Excel); (5) 9 roles interact daily = highest usage.

**P4 Contracts second** --- (1) \$8.3M outstanding debt needs visibility
NOW; (2) Document auto-generation saves Sirin/Aynur 2-3 hours daily; (3)
\$10K warning prevents costly mistakes; (4) Builds directly on P3
shipment data.

**P1 Greenhouse later** --- (1) 10 discovery questions unanswered; (2)
Mobile/offline adds complexity; (3) Current Excel works for planning;
(4) Can develop in parallel.

**6. TECHNOLOGY STACK**

  --------------------- -------------------------------------------------
  **Component**         **Technology**

  **Backend**           Django 5.x + Django REST Framework (Python 3.12)

  **Database**          Microsoft SQL Server (MSSQL) --- required for
                        Logo Tiger ERP compatibility. mssql-django
                        package.

  **Frontend**          React 18 + Ant Design Pro --- enterprise-grade UI
                        components with tables, forms, charts

  **Mobile**            Progressive Web App (PWA) for greenhouse harvest
                        input. Offline-first with service worker sync.

  **Authentication**    Django built-in + JWT tokens. 9 roles with
                        field-level permissions.

  **Real-time**         Django Channels + WebSocket for live shipment
                        status updates

  **Document Gen**      python-docx for template filling → WeasyPrint for
                        PDF output

  **GPS**               Navixy API (REST, poll every 60s). Teltonika
                        FMB920 devices on trucks.

  **Notifications**     python-telegram-bot (Telegram) + WhatsApp
                        Business API

  **Deployment**        Docker Compose: Django + React + MSSQL + Redis +
                        Nginx (5 services)

  **Development**       Claude Code multi-agent: Lead (Opus) + sub-agents
                        (Sonnet) per module
  --------------------- -------------------------------------------------

**6.1 MSSQL Constraints (All Projects)**

  ------------------------ ----------------------------------------------
  **Constraint**           **Solution**

  No JSONField /           Separate model fields or related tables
  ArrayField               

  No DISTINCT ON           Subquery with ROW_NUMBER() window function

  2,100 parameter limit    bulk_create(batch_size=500)

  Turkmen/Russian text     Per-field collation: Cyrillic_General_CI_AS or
                           Latin_General_CI_AS
  ------------------------ ----------------------------------------------

