**Minimum viable team: 2 developers + 1 analyst** (existing). Optimal: 3
developers + 1 analyst + 0.5 QA.

**AI-assisted development:** Using Claude Code with multi-agent
orchestration can accelerate development by 30-50%, effectively making a
2-person team perform like 3.

